Model ConversionConvert PyTorch model to ONNX:python convert_model/convert_to_onnx.pyConvert ONNX model to Intermediate Representation (IR):bash convert_model/convert_to_ir.shInferenceRun inference using the IR model:python inference/run_inference.pyFine-TuningFine-tune the GPT-2 model:python fine_tuning/fine_tune_model.pyContributorssyed touseef ali: Project management, architecture design, and optimization strategy.vishnu biradar: Model preparation, conversion, and fine-tuning.parmeshwar: Implementation of inference pipeline and deployment.syed touseef ali: Comprehensive documentation and user guides.### 6. requirements.txt
List of required Python packages.torch transformers numpy openvinoThis code base provides a comprehensive set of scripts for converting, optimizing, running inference, and fine-tuning LLM models using Intel® OpenVINO™ and PyTorch.
